RUN apt update -y && apt install --no-install-recommends -y g++ gcc git curl wget nasm yasm libgtk-3-dev clang libxcb-randr0-dev libxdo-dev libxfixes-dev libxcb-shape0-dev libxcb-xfixes0-dev libasound2-dev libpulse-dev cmake unzip zip sudo libgstreamer1.0-dev libgstreamer-plugins-base1.0-dev

RUN /vcpkg/bootstrap-vcpkg.sh -disableMetrics

RUN curl --proto '=https' --tlsv1.2 -sSf https://sh.rustup.rs > rustup.sh

RUN ./rustup.sh -y

USER root
ENV HOME=/home/user
COPY ./entrypoint /
ENTRYPOINT ["/entrypoint"]
